==选举结果==
初期的选举结果表明，[[蒙塞夫·马尔祖基|蒙塞夫·马尔祖基]]和[[贝吉·卡伊德·埃塞卜西|贝吉·卡伊德·埃塞卜西]]进入决选。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Tunisian presidential election set for run-off between Essebsi and Marzouki|url=http://english.al-akhbar.com/content/tunisian-presidential-election-set-run-between-essebsi-and-marzouki|agency=AFP, Reuters,Al-Akhbar|date=2014-11-24|accessdate=2014-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150204122053/http://english.al-akhbar.com/content/tunisian-presidential-election-set-run-between-essebsi-and-marzouki|archive-date=2015-02-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>[[哈马·哈马米|哈马·哈马米]]排在第三。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://english.ahram.org.eg/News/116275.aspx|title=Tunisia presidential runoff likely after 'historic' vote|agency=AFP|date=2014-11-24|accessdate=2014-11-24|archive-date=2014-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141208011051/http://english.ahram.org.eg/News/116275.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>

埃塞卜西获得突尼斯北部多数省的支持，处于领先地位，马尔祖基则在突尼斯南部各省得到多数选票，哈马米在[[锡勒亚奈省|锡勒亚奈省]]赢得大多数的选票。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.businessnews.com.tn/tunisie--resultats-partiels-pour-lelection-presidentielle-maj,520,51460,3 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-11-26 |archive-date=2014-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129083342/http://www.businessnews.com.tn/tunisie--resultats-partiels-pour-lelection-presidentielle-maj,520,51460,3 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

